            h2#chapter6 6. Recommendations
           
            p  Another option of SOR from the left side of the screen is Recommendations. Practically this offers the opportunity to receive random recommendations of Books, Films and Educational Institutes based on the user Google account.
            p One of the most interesting type of recommendation is for Films. The search basically returns films based on books that have status read/reading in Google account.  
            p 
                img(src="images/reco_films_1.png" alt="sor")
            
            h2#chapter7 7.  Logout
            p Lastly, to leave the application, use the Log out option from the top right side of the screen. This signs out from user’s account.
            
            h2#chapter8 8. Conclusion
            p As a conclusion, Social Recommender is a web application that user social networks (Google) and other external resources to recommend the user certain places, educational institutions, books and films.
            p Feel free to check out SOR!
           
